query:
SELECT
                clba.library_unit_build_id as build_id,
                co.key as object_key,
                clba.path,
                clba.mtime,
                clba.executable
            FROM cargo_library_unit_build_artifact clba
            JOIN cargo_object co ON clba.object_id = co.id
            WHERE clba.library_unit_build_id = ANY($1)
